<br />Three versions were reviewed in <em>Nintendo Power</em>: <ol style="list-style-type: decimal"><li>A Game Boy version </li><li>A Super Game Boy version, which contained both a Game Boy version and a Super NES version </li><li>A Super NES version, which also had a 2-player simultaneous mode </li></ol>

		

