		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />(using names given in <a href="http://www.rawer.de/marc/Gameboy/Docs/Sgb.txt" class="postlink">Sgb.txt</a>)
<br />
<br />I'm guessing Super NES WRAM Transfer ($0F, $10), GameBoy Window Mask ($17), and Set Program Counter ($12). The format for "CharSet Transfer" tiles is exactly the same as the normal Super NES or PC Engine tile format.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
